      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s in absolute mint condition and has been my total pride and joy. Honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom\u2014spotless interior, flawless paint, and it runs like a dream. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
