    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a showroom. This car boasts a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of even the smallest stone chips or swirls. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats are supple and show zero signs of wear, while the original floor mats look untouched. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively garage-kept and serviced ahead of schedule at certified dealerships. Complete with a full service history and two sets of keys, this is a turnkey opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection. It drives as smoothly as it looks, offering a tight, responsive experience that confirms its meticulous upkeep.",
      "price": 48500.0,
